############
Installation
############

This project is open-source, published under BSD license.
See :doc:`/about/license` for details.

If you want to install a development environment, you should go to
:doc:`/contribute/index` documentation.

.. code-block:: sh

   # Download and install (in a virtualenv if you like).
   pip install diecutter
   # Configure: adapt "YOUR_TEMPLATE_DIR"!
   wget -O diecutter.ini --post-data "template_dir=YOUR_TEMPLATE_DIR" http://diecutter.alwaysdata.net/diecutter.ini
   # Run the server.
   pserve diecutter.ini --reload

Check it works:

.. code-block:: text

   $ curl http://localhost:8106
   {"diecutter": "Hello", "version": "0.1dev"}
